{"tid":2158622,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「白俄羅斯」與「Xianggang」的距離","createTime":"2020-08-15T21:05:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-17T18:04:42.000Z","uid":359022,"like":53,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"9d7bf501bc11912e2c36aad9cb11faa1c188fa79","tid":2158622,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T21:05:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/白俄羅斯與xianggang的距離/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%E7%99%BD%E4%BF%84%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AF%E8%88%87xianggang%E7%9A%84%E8%B7%9D%E9%9B%A2%2F&d=Z4osEZd2TI9THLKNWu9EL7ccVloK1XwbfTGMhSGe0oU%3D&h=bb088194\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%E7%99%BD%E4%BF%84%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AF%E8%88%87xianggang%E7%9A%84%E8%B7%9D%E9%9B%A2%2F&h=68a09e16\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/international/白俄羅斯與xianggang的距離/</a><br />\n<br />\n討論 Belarus 抗爭，記得用返「白羅斯」，唔好用「白俄羅斯」啊！人哋就係唔想同俄羅斯黐咁埋，特登改官方中文譯名。<br />\n<br />\n對白羅斯抗爭者而言，「白俄羅斯」就好似「Xianggang」咁難聽。"},{"pid":"3b4e18e5c0abb61500438c81383c910522b054da","tid":2158622,"uid":273703,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T21:06:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f861ee451b6cded57249ba25116286f6609c7a90","tid":2158622,"uid":154486,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T21:07:18.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">誠懇呼籲唔好舉呢支旗</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n白羅斯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HJHMqRp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHJHMqRp.jpg&h=624029b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nsource國際文宣組tg<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vOGxmpN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvOGxmpN.jpg&h=355979b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QGQ2JC8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQGQ2JC8.png&h=bdae0503&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1991年白羅斯自蘇聯獨立後，曾於1992年立法恢復使用1918年至1920年白羅斯人民共和國時的白紅白雙色三條式國旗。<br />\n<br />\n直到1995年因為白羅斯強人總統盧卡申科的親俄背景，改採白俄羅斯蘇維埃社會主義共和國國旗，將該旗稍做修改（取消蘇聯時期的金色鐮刀錘子及金邊紅色五角星圖案）後即成為現在的樣式。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%99%BD%E4%BF%84%E7%BD%97%E6%96%AF%E5%9B%BD%E6%97%97\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E7%2599%25BD%25E4%25BF%2584%25E7%25BD%2597%25E6%2596%25AF%25E5%259B%25BD%25E6%2597%2597&d=Z4osEZd2TI9THLKNWu9EL7ccVloK1XwbfTGMhSGe0oU%3D&h=48c9385e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%99%BD%E4%BF%84%E7%BD%97%E6%96%AF%E5%9B%BD%E6%97%97</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">呢D反白倒盧既旗<br />\n大家千祈唔好因為手痕以為人地唔識就Print出黎周圍貼</span>"},{"pid":"d6c4cf645927f71846088e2105c8819b3f827b8e","tid":2158622,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T21:18:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35401d6b33f2c8ce6dd46a453242b0e079e2c80b","tid":2158622,"uid":183844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T21:24:53.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"63516e2085b95030e14a965d554f396ff0ccc301","tid":2158622,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T21:35:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2097276ccb88da0d7471626f1f70d8739838c4d","tid":215